Name: Commandant's Lounge
Desc: Entrance to the Commandant's exclusive lounge. The sliding door is equipped with a state-of-the-art iris recognition system.

Name: Construction Square
Desc: The business development plan has encountered mysterious resistance. In the time of crisis, the Gray Raven Commandant is appointed as Chief Commissioner, granted full authority to oversee the plan's implementation and investigate the mastermind lurking behind the scenes...

Name: Manage the Cafe
Desc: Kuroro Coffee used to be one of the most popular leisure destinations, but recently its business hasn't been going so well. What troubles has Manager Ross encountered? The storm brewing in the coffee cup is about to unfold...

Name: Under the Astral Canopy
Desc: Sequence Square serves as the hub for all commercial activities in the Commercial District, while the Astral Canopy stands witness to Babylonia's prosperity.

Name: Square Corridor
Desc: A corridor leading directly to Sequence Square. Though it appears somewhat deserted, it serves as an essential transit route for commuting within the ship.

Name: Space Leap
Desc: A VR device from Stellar Entertainment that shot to fame with its generous ranking rewards. Players are loving it—just as the company promises: Thrilling! Fun! Safe!

Name: Kuroro Coffee
Desc: A popular coffee shop in the Commercial District, run by Ross, an experienced shop owner.

Name: Restaurant Entrance
Desc: A bustling Kowloong-themed restaurant where you can almost smell the enticing aroma of stir-fried dishes just by standing at the entrance.

Name: Street Corner Leisure Area
Desc: A public leisure area attached to Orbital Corridor, which provides great convenience for shoppers.

Name: Ship Elevator - 3F
Desc: A high-speed elevator made from carbon nanofibers and powered by superconductive materials. This is the 3rd floor stop.

Name: Ship Elevator - 1F
Desc: A high-speed elevator made from carbon nanofibers and powered by superconductive materials. This is the 1st floor stop.

Name: Stella Brew
Desc: A widely acclaimed leisure facility renowned for its exquisite specialty drinks.

Name: Ring Avenue
Desc: The Commercial Square is accessible from all directions, making it a true hub of Babylonia.

Name: Space Leap
Desc: A VR device from Stellar Entertainment that shot to fame with its generous ranking rewards. Players are loving it—just as the company promises: Thrilling! Fun! Safe!
